casebody.data:
APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2013-0152. Bank of New York v. Elliot.

Cuyahoga App. Nos. 97506 and 98179, 2012-Ohio-5285. Upon consideration of the jurisdictional memoranda filed in this case, the court declines to accept jurisdiction of the appeal pursuant to S.CtPrac.R. 7.08(B)(4).
